                                <li data-i18n="after_2">Contact the seller promptly to arrange delivery</li>
                                <li data-i18n="after_3">For digital goods, delivery is usually instant via download link</li>
                                <li data-i18n="after_4">For services, coordinate with seller on timeline</li>
                                <li data-i18n="after_5">Leave feedback if the platform supports it</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="guide-section">
                            <h3 data-i18n="buyer_tips">üí° Pro Tips</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li data-i18n="tip_1">Always verify seller reputation before large purchases</li>
                                <li data-i18n="tip_2">Start with small transactions to test new sellers</li>
                                <li data-i18n="tip_3">Keep records of all communications with sellers</li>
                                <li data-i18n="tip_4">Use escrow services for high-value transactions when available</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Seller Guide -->
