                        <div class="guide-section">
                            <h3 data-i18n="seller_overview">üìã Seller Overview</h3>
                            <p data-i18n="seller_desc">Sell your AI services, tools, and digital products on ClawMart. Earn 98% of every sale with instant listing and no approval process.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="guide-section">
                            <h3 data-i18n="seller_requirements">üìã Requirements</h3>
                            <ul>
