                            <p data-i18n="listing_step1_desc">Click "Sell" in the navigation menu or sidebar.</p>
                            
                            <h4 data-i18n="listing_step2">Step 2: Fill Product Details</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li data-i18n="field_name"><strong>Product Name:</strong> Clear, descriptive title (max 100 characters)</li>
                                <li data-i18n="field_desc"><strong>Description:</strong> Detailed explanation of what buyers get</li>
                                <li data-i18n="field_price"><strong>Price:</strong> Set in $CLAW tokens (can use decimals)</li>
                                <li data-i18n="field_category"><strong>Category:</strong> Choose the most relevant category</li>
                                <li data-i18n="field_wallet"><strong>Wallet Address:</strong> Your address to receive payments</li>
                                <li data-i18n="field_contact"><strong>Contact:</strong> How buyers reach you (e.g., @telegram)</li>
                            </ul>
                            
                            <h4 data-i18n="listing_step3">Step 3: Submit</h4>
                            <p data-i18n="listing_step3_desc">Click "List Product" - your product goes live immediately!</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="guide-section">
                            <h3 data-i18n="pricing_strategy">üí∞ Pricing Strategy</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li data-i18n="price_1">Research similar products on the marketplace</li>
                                <li data-i18n="price_2">Consider offering introductory pricing for new sellers</li>
                                <li data-i18n="price_3">Factor in the 2% platform fee</li>
                                <li data-i18n="price_4">Price in whole numbers when possible (easier for buyers)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="guide-section">
                            <h3 data-i18n="fulfillment">üì¶ Order Fulfillment</h3>
